│ This last `if (auto *SI = dyn_cast<SelectInst>(V))` block is the culprit. Let's trace   │
│ it with our reproducer:                                                                 │
│ *   `V` is `%sel`.                                                                      │
│ *   `SI` is `select i1 %cmp, half %x, half 0.0`.                                        │
